description: This skill allows users to search for Klingon words by English, to fetch random Klingon sayings, to lookup today's Klingon Word of the Day, and to learn more about Klingons and the Klingon language. Content provided by Hol 'ampaS, the Klingon Assault Group's Language Academy.
exampleInteractions: alexa ask klingon dictionary to tell me a random proverb
alexa ask klingon dictionary for today's word
name: Klingon Dictionary
shortDescription: Gives access to Klingon language resources
